name: RoboPrint OA 01 SW
description:
RoboPrint OA 01 SW is part of the Series: '4 ISO Views of: Open Architecture 01' - Edition 3/3. by @grasser_alex alexandergrasser.com 
Designed at my realtime architecture platform, it embeds multiple local design decisions of distributed architects. A multi-subjective and multi-objective collaborative whole, an open architecture of collaborative objects. It's drawn with archival ink using a Rotrics Robot, on a 30 x 30 cm 220gsm Lana Dessin Paper. 
This nft comes with the original drawing, international shipping included. Upon resale on the secondary market the original drawing shall be sent to the new owner. Shipping will be covered by the new owner
